clubText: The mission of the FHS Gender & Sexuality Alliance (GSA) is to foster pride, create a safe harbor, empower the lonely, fortify the weak, and engage in learning about LGBTQIA+ history and current events. We believe a diverse school community prepares us for life in a dynamic world, and we celebrate what unites us and what makes us unique. We support the intersectionality of all identity affinity clubs that strive for diversity, equity, and inclusion.
